accessControlMaxAgeSec.description: A number that CloudFront uses as the value for the `max-age` directive in the `Strict-Transport-Security` HTTP response header.

includeSubdomains.description: Whether CloudFront includes the `includeSubDomains` directive in the `Strict-Transport-Security` HTTP response header.

override.description: Whether CloudFront overrides the `Strict-Transport-Security` HTTP response header received from the origin with the one specified in this response headers policy.

preload.description: Whether CloudFront includes the `preload` directive in the `Strict-Transport-Security` HTTP response header.
